  "title": "Beauty Therapist",
  "description": "<p>Job Highlights</p><ul><li>Career Progression</li><li>Various team and individual bonuses</li><li>Positive and fun work environment</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Descriptions:</strong></p><ul><li>Provide hair removal treatments.</li><li>Provide excellent recommendation on treatment, packages and products to clients</li><li>Explaining all treatment procedures to clients.</li><li>Advise clients on pre and post treatment care.</li><li>Establish good rapport and to give professional advise to potential and existing clients.</li><li>Prepare of treatment rooms, maintain cleanliness and neatness of work station.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Candidates with no experience are welcome to apply</li><li>Those with waxing or sugaring background previously would be a bonus</li><li>Good communication skills</li></ul><p><strong>Job Details and Benefits:</strong></p><ul><li>Attractive salary package plus lucrative commission ranging from $1,600 to $4,000 (depending on experience and qualification)</li><li>Training will be provided</li><li>Positive working environment</li><li>Nearby MRT</li><li>Annual salary increment (based on performance)</li><li>Annual bonus entitlement (based on performance)</li><li>Operation Hours (Cavan): Mondays-Friday (11am to 8pm), Saturday (10am to 6pm) & Sunday & PH (11am to 6pm)</li><li>Operation Hours (malls): Mondays-Sundays (10am to 10pm) [mix of opening and closing shift]</li><li>5.5 working days in a week (based on shift)</li><li>Group hospital and surgical benefit for outpatient and inpatient care.</li><li>GP Clinic (IHP)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Interested candidates kindly send your resume to</p><p>hr.sugarwaxed@gmail.com or cavan.sugarwaxed@gmail.com</p><p><br /></p><p>Alternatively, you may <strong>Call </strong>or <strong>WhatsApp +65 9800 3002 </strong>(Jack) for an interview.</p><p><br /></p><p>www.sugarwaxed.com</p>",
